<h3>Get Businesses GraphQL</h3>
<ul>
    <li><a asp-action="TestGetGraphQlAsync">Test GetGraphQlAsync - 30 restaurants retrieved via one GraphQL call in about 4-5 seconds.</a></li>
    <li><a asp-action="TestGetGraphQlInChunksAsync">Test GetGraphQlInChunksAsync - 30 restaurants retrieved via multiple GraphQL calls (25 restaurants per call) made in parallel in about 2-3 seconds.</a></li>
</ul>

